{"tid":1418982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一張圖屌哂啲分化撚 意志唔堅定嘅人","createTime":"2019-08-05T22:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:09:14.000Z","uid":191532,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c73fcf253bd82ccd31ac40063bf4ef2e1fec3fa0","tid":1418982,"uid":191532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Njp8VsD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNjp8VsD.png&h=f0bd4c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地而家對抗緊個政府 話咩前線變到好似速龍咁 起火又屌 嗌口號又屌 話我地前線唔理性嘅究竟有無上過前睇我地做左啲咩</span></span><br />\nBtw講翻戰術上 個人認為游擊唔係問題 但係可唔可以唔好行到老閪咁遠 你未對到狗 次次自己人搬野都搬死 有時覺得你佔左一度好似今日龍翔道 下午就開行turbo同佢死過仲有效 次次一拖到夜晚 啲狗就增援 我地視野又差根本無得打 <br />\n<br />\n講到尾 和理 勇武 缺一不可 我地而家唔係普通遊行 即使你唔覺得我地係革命緊 但係都希望大家出得尼比翻小小勇氣 決心自己 同自己講我地唔係玩 我地追求公義先企出尼 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可能我地做嘅野唔係啱哂 但係我地會認錯 呢個就係我地同政府黑警嘅分別</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代<span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"124a95c069849ddfd12ecf23485dbe92fba55deb","tid":1418982,"uid":191532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:36:21.000Z","msg":"推到所有人堅定一致"},{"pid":"48685dd80f9194f8f2c6485550a5f3c8e7a149f0","tid":1418982,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b684eb12ea6758f903ce4b55deca13746ea38b","tid":1418982,"uid":266993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:43:32.000Z","msg":"可以提出意見 但唔好屌前線 講完"},{"pid":"d20f64a3a32aa453193b82133cea4099ed0b6ce1","tid":1418982,"uid":191532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1b684eb12ea6758f903ce4b55deca13746ea38b","tid":1418982,"uid":266993,"like":0,"dislike":0,